  <_name>ColorHug CCMX Loader</_name>
  <_summary>Modify the calibration matrices on the ColorHug device</_summary>
  <description>
    <_p>
      The ColorHug CCMX loader tool automatically downloads and installs
      user-submitted device correction matrices onto your Hughski ColorHug
      display colorimeter.
    </_p>
    <_p>
      Selecting a correction matrix maximises the accuracy of the ColorHug but
      using the default matrix will give most users an acceptable calibration
      result.
    </_p>
  </description>
